query:
INSERT INTO plan_questions (
                    id,
                    task_id,
                    question_id,
                    question_text,
                    category,
                    required,
                    suggested_answers
                ) VALUES ($1, $2, $3, $4, $5, $6, $7)
                RETURNING
                    id as "id!: Uuid",
                    task_id as "task_id!: Uuid",
                    question_id,
                    question_text,
                    category as "category!: QuestionCategory",
                    required as "required!: bool",
                    suggested_answers,
                    created_at as "created_at!: DateTime<Utc>"
